(Mandatory Requirements) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Bid security must equal 2% of the contract value and remain valid for at least 120) Tj
T*
(days from submission.) Tj
T*
(2. The operator portal, resident notification templates, and enforcement officer) Tj
T*
(interface must support Arabic and English.) Tj
T*
(3. The hosted production service must achieve at least 99.5% monthly uptime, excluding) Tj
T*
(scheduled maintenance approved 72 hours in advance.) Tj
T*
(4. The supplier must provide evidence of ISO 27001 certification, SOC 2 Type II, or an) Tj
T*
(equivalent independent security audit completed within the last 18 months.) Tj
T*
(5. Production go-live for the five pilot districts must be completed no later than 30) Tj
T*
(September 2026.) Tj
T*
(6. All resident personal data and plate metadata must be stored in data centers) Tj
T*
(physically located in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.) Tj
T*
